creator: Michael Thaler
descriptionHtml:
An application to manage knitting projects:
- manage a list of knitting projects
- filter list using categories
- record time needed to create a knitting
- take photos of knitting project and store them
- Set photo as preview for knitting list
- Export all knitting projects including details and photos to Dropbox and import them again on the same phone / a different phone

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
- Only replace photo with compressed photo if size is actually smaller
- Check if photo exists when exporting to Dropbox
